classDiagram
    direction LR

    class EcosystemQueryKeeper {
        <<x/ecosystem (只读)>> 
        -tokenomicsKeeper TokenomicsKeeper
        -phonenodeKeeper PhonenodeKeeper
        -edgeaiKeeper EdgeaiKeeper
        -depinKeeper DepinKeeper
        +QueryOverview(ctx) OverviewResp
        +QueryNodeDetail(ctx, addr) NodeDetailResp
        +QueryTaskDetail(ctx, id) TaskDetailResp
    }

    class TokenomicsKeeper {
        <<read-only interface>>
        +GetMintedSupply(ctx) sdk.Int
        +GetAllocations(ctx) []PoolAllocation
    }

    class PhonenodeKeeper {
        <<read-only interface>>
        +GetNode(ctx, addr) *NodeState
        +HasNode(ctx, addr) bool
        +IsAttested(ctx, addr) bool
        +GetAttestation(ctx, addr) Attestation
        +CountNodes(ctx) int
    }

    class EdgeaiKeeper {
        <<read-only interface>>
        +GetTask(ctx, id) *Task
        +GetResult(ctx, taskId) *Result
        +GetDispute(ctx, id) *Dispute
        +CountTasks(ctx) int
    }

    class DepinKeeper {
        <<read-only interface>>
        +GetDevice(ctx, addr) *Device
        +CountDevices(ctx) int
    }

    class StandardEvent {
        <<约定 topic>>
        mcchain.tokenomics.{Mint,Allocation}
        mcchain.depin.{Contribution,Payout}
        mcchain.phonenode.{Attestation,Slash,StateProof}
        mcchain.edgeai.{TaskCreated,ResultAccepted,Dispute,Resolved}
    }

    class OffChainContracts {
        <<docs/*.md 链下>>
        sdk_contract / explorer_contract
        wallet_contract / depin_demand_contract
    }

    EcosystemQueryKeeper --> TokenomicsKeeper : 只读聚合
    EcosystemQueryKeeper --> PhonenodeKeeper : 只读聚合
    EcosystemQueryKeeper --> EdgeaiKeeper : 只读聚合
    EcosystemQueryKeeper --> DepinKeeper : 只读聚合
    StandardEvent ..> OffChainContracts : 订阅消费
    OffChainContracts ..> PhonenodeKeeper : 钱包复用 B4 proof
    OffChainContracts ..> EdgeaiKeeper : DePIN 复用 B3 任务类型

    note for EcosystemQueryKeeper "纯只读：无状态/无Msg/无BeginBlock/无模块账户；绝不 MintCoins"
    note for StandardEvent "前缀 mcchain.<module>.<Event>；状态变更点 EmitEvent"
    note for OffChainContracts "链下契约，本批次不实现"
